step 0 ⚡ Run updated SQL
Run schema-part4-rls.sql in Supabase SQL Editor. This fixes the RLS policies.

Test 1: Homepage & Public Pages
Go to http://localhost:3000 → see the full landing page
Go to /blog, /faq, /contact → should all render with content
Test 2: Signup (Individual Seeker)
Go to /signup
Pick 🇸🇦 Saudi Arabia → I need legal services → Individual → enter name, email, password
Check email → confirm → check Supabase profiles table: should have account_cat=seeker, s_type=individual
Test 3: Login & Individual Dashboard
Go to /login → sign in with the Individual account
Should redirect to /dashboard/seeker/individual
You should see:
✅ Green sidebar with 5 menu items (Dashboard, AI Chat, Browse, My Cases, Wallet)
✅ Welcome message with your name
✅ Quick action cards (Consultation, Contract Review, Find Lawyer, Track Cases)
✅ Stats showing 0s
✅ "Create New Request" button
Test 4: Create a Service Request
Click "إنشاء طلب جديد" (or the Consultation quick action)
Pick a category, enter title like "Need help with employment contract"
Click Submit Request
The request should appear below in "My Cases" with a timeline tracker
Test 5: Signup (Independent Lawyer)
Sign out → go to /signup with a different email
Pick 🇸🇦 Saudi Arabia → I provide legal services → Independent Lawyer → enter details
Confirm email → check profiles table: account_cat=provider, p_type=independent_lawyer
Test 6: Lawyer Dashboard
Login as the Lawyer → should redirect to /dashboard/provider/independent_lawyer
You should see:
✅ Green sidebar with 7 menu items
✅ Tabbed layout (Overview / Inbox / Board / Community)
✅ Profile card on the right
✅ In the Inbox tab: the request from Test 4 should appear under "Available Pool Requests"
Click ✅ to accept it → it moves to "My Requests"
Switch to Board tab → see it in the "In Progress" column
Test 7: Language & Dark Mode
Click 🌐 in the topbar → UI switches between Arabic/English
Click 🌙 → dark mode toggle
Click the sign out button (🚪) → returns to homepage